---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
---
<Layout title="About — CNY vs LNY">
  <Navbar />
  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="font-serif text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-8">About</h1>

    <p class="text-lg text-text-muted mb-4">Words carry history, identity, and context.</p>

    <p class="text-text-muted mb-4">Each year, institutions choose different terms to refer to this holiday. Rather than debate intentions, this project records usage.</p>

    <p class="text-text-muted mb-8">By documenting how organizations refer to the holiday, we aim to encourage thoughtful discussion grounded in observable facts.</p>

    <hr class="border-[rgba(240,230,255,0.1)] my-10" />

    <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold mb-6">This Is Not a Boycott List</h2>

    <p class="text-text-muted mb-4">This project exists solely to document publicly observable terminology choices. It does <strong>not</strong> endorse, encourage, or facilitate boycotts, harassment, or any targeted action against organisations based on the term they use.</p>

    <p class="text-text-muted mb-4">We believe organisations are free to choose whatever terminology they consider appropriate. The dataset is intended for research, education, and informed discussion &mdash; not to pressure, shame, or punish any entity.</p>

    <p class="text-text-muted mb-8">Blog posts and opinion pieces hosted on this site represent the views of their individual authors and do not reflect the position of the project.</p>

    <hr class="border-[rgba(240,230,255,0.1)] my-10" />

    <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold mb-6">中文版本</h2>

    <p class="text-text-muted mb-4" lang="zh">本网站记录各机构、媒体与组织在今年对该节日所使用的称呼（Chinese New Year / Lunar New Year）。</p>

    <p class="text-text-muted mb-4" lang="zh">我们不参与立场争论，只做客观记录。</p>

    <p class="text-text-muted mb-4" lang="zh">通过公开透明的数据，帮助讨论建立在事实基础之上。</p>

    <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-bold mb-4" lang="zh">本项目不是抵制名单</h3>

    <p class="text-text-muted mb-4" lang="zh">本项目仅记录各机构公开使用的节日称呼，<strong>不</strong>支持、鼓励或协助任何形式的抵制、骚扰或针对性行动。各机构有权自行选择其认为合适的称呼。本站所载博客和评论文章仅代表作者个人观点，不代表项目立场。</p>
  </main>
</Layout>
